    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Ubuntu使用Terminator作为默认终端]]></title>
    <link href="http://lvxudong.com/blog/2014/03/01/ubuntu-change-default-terminal/"/>
    <updated>2014-03-01T13:44:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://lvxudong.com/blog/2014/03/01/ubuntu-change-default-terminal</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3>首先安装Terminator</h3>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>sudo apt-get install terminator</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h3>安装dconf-tools</h3>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>sudo apt-get install dconf-tools</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h3>配置为默认终端</h3>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>gsettings set org.gnome.desktop.default-applications.terminal exec /usr/bin/terminator
</span><span class='line'>gsettings set org.gnome.desktop.default-applications.terminal exec-arg "-x"</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h3>开始享有功能强大的Terminator吧</h3>
]]></content>
